            <h2>üéØ What Inbox Zero Really Means</h2>
            
            <div class="insight-box">
                <h3>Inbox Zero ‚â† Zero Emails</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
                    Inbox Zero isn't about having no emails. It's about having zero unprocessed emails. Every email in your inbox has been consciously decided upon and either acted on or appropriately organized.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin: 40px 0;">
