                    <div style="background: #fee2e2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
                        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li><strong>"Delete everything"</strong> - Missing important information</li>
                            <li><strong>"Respond immediately"</strong> - Reactive, not strategic</li>
                            <li><strong>"Perfect organization"</strong> - Spending more time organizing than doing</li>
                            <li><strong>"Never-ending task"</strong> - Requires constant maintenance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h3 style="color: #10b981; text-align: center;">‚úÖ GTD Inbox Zero Reality</h3>
