                        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li><strong>"Process everything"</strong> - Every email gets a conscious decision</li>
                            <li><strong>"Strategic action"</strong> - Do what's appropriate when it's appropriate</li>
                            <li><strong>"Functional organization"</strong> - Simple system that actually works</li>
                            <li><strong>"Daily habit"</strong> - 20 minutes of processing keeps you current</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
