                <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">The 2-minute rule is the heart of efficient email processing:</p>
                
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fecfef); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <h4 style="font-size: 1.3em; margin-bottom: 15px;">If it takes less than 2 minutes to complete, DO IT NOW</h4>
                    <p>This prevents small tasks from accumulating into overwhelming piles while maintaining processing momentum.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
