                        <h4>‚úÖ Good 2-Minute Actions:</h4>
                        <ul style="margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                            <li>Quick "yes/no" responses</li>
                            <li>Forwarding with brief note</li>
                            <li>Adding to calendar</li>
                            <li>Filing reference material</li>
                            <li>Quick status updates</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <h4>‚ùå Don't Do in 2 Minutes:</h4>
                        <ul style="margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                            <li>Thoughtful, detailed responses</li>
                            <li>Research or analysis</li>
                            <li>Complex decision-making</li>
                            <li>Creating documents</li>
                            <li>Lengthy conversations</li>
                        </ul>
